'''The Continental NYC''', originally known as '''Tower 111''', is a 53-story, 338-unit luxury rental skyscraper designed by architect [[Costas Kondylis]] in the [[New York City]] borough of [[Manhattan]] at 885 [[Sixth Avenue (Manhattan)|Sixth Avenue]] and 32nd Street in [[Midtown Manhattan]].<ref>http://ny.curbed.com/places/the-continental</ref>
